These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, tram, pokering
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, aquamarine, red, pink
4 different games are played: domino, poker, snooker, chess
1. the photographer is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person who likes red is the designer##1
4. the person driving the pokering is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the photographer is the person playing domino##1
8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
9. the person driving the pokering is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport         | trike  | pokering  | helicopter | tram |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Color   | pink       | red      | brown | aquamarine      |
| Game           | domino          | poker     | snooker    | chess     |

