.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, sudoku, woodworking, board-games
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
City: boston, paris, hannover, prague
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, quad-bike, boat
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to prague is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
9. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby      | woodworking     | gardening       | sudoku | board-games        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| City   | hannover      | paris       | prague     | boston    |
| Transport         | quad-bike | boat | bike | skateboard |

