.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, cycling, snowboarding, surfing
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, june, september, july
City: paris, berlin, liverpool, london
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the person traveling to london##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Sport      | cycling | water-polo       | surfing        | snowboarding        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Birthday   | august     | june    | july | september        |
| City           | liverpool         | paris  | london       | berlin         |

