.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, crime, adventure, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, electronic, funk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, iris, daisy, balloon-flower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, january, june
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
8. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre           | crime   | western  | superhero | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Flower   | daisy       | balloon-flower    | iris     | dahlia  |
| Birthday           | august     | january | june     | may         |

