7. the french is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
