 4. the person who likes pink is the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the person driving the train is the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
